{"tid":391161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心認真Post，食譚仔食到條撚同條米線一樣","createTime":"2017-09-07T14:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T17:45:45.000Z","uid":36776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e2265f38354f3fa2159c15ec5c30bdef4d81e298","tid":391161,"uid":36776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"我今年22歲，一個好普通岩岩u grad 既學生。諗番轉頭，食譚仔對我既危害係極大，我以前搭車上堂訓教無啦啦都會扯旗，而家變到對住條女準備入洞都扯唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係5年前Form 6 左右接觸譚仔，個時一個月都食唔到一次，直到我Year1左右樓下開左間譚仔，我食食下就開始上癮，每個星期起碼食5餐2小辣。<br />\n<br />\n持續左一年左右咁既生活，我個時都重係處男未發現到有異樣，只係發現我小便既時候多左啲餘尿，次次都柯唔清。咁我都係認為可能打得飛機多，又夜訓所以搞到咁。之後差唔多食左三年譚仔左右，我開始發現我朝早起身既時候有D唔妥，我好似好耐都冇試過晨勃，以前中學重未食譚仔既時候，朝早落床去廁所要彎住腰去，驚俾呀媽見到我扯旗，扯住柯重要驚柯到周圍都係，而家我朝早扯都唔扯重要有餘尿。同埋呢幾年打飛機都係1分鐘左右完事，唔係太硬，重好似愈黎愈幼，我都愈黎愈擔心，個時又唔知原因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到我識左我現任女朋友，大家都會一齊去食譚仔，都幾sweet嫁其實大家一齊食個套餐。我哄左成兩年終於都可以唔洗做青頭仔，個晚係佢個Hall度，出左成日街，做左1個鍾前戲，佢都濕曬嫁啦，但係我就點都扯唔起，係軟到米線個隻咁Dum落黎，咩反應都冇。之後我地放棄左，心諗我第一次緊張姐。我地之後第二次再試，終於扯得起! 不過係半軟既狀態，入都入唔到。最大穫係，最近我地第五次試既時候我竟然錫錫下射左!洩左!我呆左，我女朋友見到都好失落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無理由會咁我以前明明搭車上堂訓教朝早起身都扯到勁痕，重會俾fd笑性慾太強，自從我每星期5餐譚仔之後性能力就係咁跌，而家差唔多性無能咁濟。我岩岩先開始戒譚仔，但係一個星期都忍唔住要去食兩餐。<br />\n<br />\n我想慎重咁同咁多位巴打絲打講，食譚仔真係好傷身，男仔會食到性無能，對女仔有咩影響我唔知，不過都唔好食咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw，有冇人可以教下我點先可以恢復番我既性能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸:重係青頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/224038_5334cbe216f484830e1cdb20a89f44ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F224038_5334cbe216f484830e1cdb20a89f44ed.jpg&h=11ee7f94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩食完"},{"pid":"0fce7cd940e404414f3d939c3dc3394212a1c052","tid":391161,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"哈 笑死"},{"pid":"2562f658ce24bed02cabdc90a567e389459c9550","tid":391161,"uid":11805,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:42:46.000Z","msg":"下我睇左啲咩=.="},{"pid":"59b3758f3d81262d153f863a4dd6fa7e1c534e60","tid":391161,"uid":36776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"我講真"},{"pid":"58a8ddabe269e6736b59b6c2f6022c1674843e2e","tid":391161,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠哂彈性"},{"pid":"2c8dd621fde40ae7317f4deae091fe7673f23dfa","tid":391161,"uid":135060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T14:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你條撚咪可以咁玩"},{"pid":"49080ee3cb40fe9f7e3207ddb2a9d1dc9030b43e","tid":391161,"uid":36776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你條撚咪可以咁玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉，重慘過咁樣，冇咁長"},{"pid":"c72d453f793f2c79bfb987fd01342a983bd17fd8","tid":391161,"uid":7645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:05:25.000Z","msg":"每日做提肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5704acf77012dbb1c79a7ebd536e52e75edc90ed","tid":391161,"uid":132470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:08:49.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲以為有得睇同米線一樣咁幼既撚"},{"pid":"19d0ee2d5a3cf8bee50d1d57e89bdf2ea9a5bd14","tid":391161,"uid":76939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣，但係無食譚仔習慣，但之前試過每日都打丁。依家先year 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc28d63182e051c32b8029fe6329b58d9583cdc3","tid":391161,"uid":79036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁大獲"}]}